Snowboarding in Morocco? Yes please! 🇲🇦

 “One place I never thought my snowboard would take me is Africa. That all changed recently when my old friend @Mariachi_d called and asked if I wanted to join her on a Moroccan snow adventure. I couldn’t resist, and shortly thereafter we were boarding a flight to Marrakech. The funny thing is, Maria and I didn't plan anything before we arrived. We didn't know where to go or how we would get there. Letting fate decide how or when we would get up to the mountains. Luckily, we met @mohamedoujanda at the @gite_taouraout and he dialed us in with a route that would (hopefully) get us into some snow! We hiked 16km to the base Jbel Ayachi, which would serve as our base camp. Taking tours and exploring different parts of the mountain, we were able to find some amazing lines. It was a trip of going with the flow, we completely immersed ourselves in Moroccan culture and terrain. What an experience!” - @kaitlynfarr 

#alwayschasingthesun #costatequila #morroccosnow #snowboarding #africa #travelstories
